name: RDU2 Labor Tracking Tool
description: Adds Calm Code Buttons into the FCLM Labor Tracking Kiosk. This has been updated to include CAP, Inbound, Outbound, Ship Dock, HR, Safety and Learning. This was written with the intention to help PGs, PAs, AM, Trainers, Safety Team Members and HR Members to better assist with Labor Tracking.  Any changes or additions please message via slack to blelliot@. Hopes this helps everyone! Code taken and inspired from jeickels@, dkingamz@, salloumr@, @blelliot edited by @trixiefe.
